body:
Hey so

Yes the ending was awful. I understand why no one likes it and why it was complete shit.

BUT

there really is no reason to sign a fucking petition to reshoot it. There are too many other important things to worry about rn and also, the crew and actors and everyone else (other than D&D) have worked so hard to give us the best they could that it’s honestly kinda disrespectful for us to consider making them do it again just so we’re satisfied. It’s done. Let it die. Thanks for coming to my ted talk.
